--- title: "Programming basics" format: html: toc: false section-divs: true include-after-body: - text: | --- ### Welcome to R! {.no-hide} R is easiest to use when you know how the R language works. This tutorial will teach you the implicit background knowledge that informs every piece of R code. You'll learn about: * **functions** and their **arguments** * **objects** * R's basic **data types** * R's basic data structures including **vectors** and **lists** * R's **package system** ##
